Data.#text: whoami - displays logged on user information

"powershell.exe" & {$Manufacturer = Get-WmiObject -Class Win32_ComputerSystem | select-object -expandproperty \""Manufacturer\"", $Model = Get-WmiObject -Class Win32_ComputerSystem | select-object -expandproperty \""Model\"", if((($Manufacturer.ToLower() -eq \""microsoft corporation\"") -and ($Model.ToLower().contains(\""virtual\""))) -or ($Manufacturer.ToLower().contains(\""vmware\"")) -or ($Model.ToLower() -eq \""virtualbox\"")) {write-host \""Virtualization environment detected!\""} else {write-host \""No virtualization environment detected!\""}}
